---
description: Internationalization conventions
globs: apps/web/src/i18n/**, apps/web/src/locales/**
alwaysApply: false
---
# i18n

- German is the primary UI language; English resources are kept ready for post-MVP.
- Add new user-facing strings to locale resource files.
- Use stable translation keys grouped by feature namespace.
- Avoid concatenating translated fragments; pass variables to interpolation instead.
